For achieving higher CRI, the emission spectrum should be as broad as it can. On the other hand, the broader the emission spectrum, the luminance efficacy of radiation (LER) will be low. The trade-off between CRI and LER is usually represented using the following function that optimizes CRI and LER25.1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
